{"tid":2304840,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"市建局「煥然懿居」超額認購113倍","createTime":"2020-11-29T06:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T02:42:12.000Z","uid":212249,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbd89495ed5887985c59c96f9671dfa63a4268f","tid":2304840,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】市建局港人首次置業先導項目「煥然懿居」貨尾43個單位，接獲逾4900份申請，超額認購113倍。<br />\n<br />\n市建局表示，一人及家庭申請者，分別佔五成八及四成二，近九成申請者屬八十後及九十後。<br />\n<br />\n43個單位以市價七折出售，市建局預計下個月下旬，電腦隨機排序定出申請者選購單位的優先次序，並依次安排見面。<br />\n<br />\n市建局同時考慮，將觀塘安達臣道第二個「首置」項目加快工程進度，期望將預售年期推前至2023年。"},{"pid":"b0807999a398f7a60f6e491e5ab4463417570607","tid":2304840,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:59:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414701&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=5cb01c05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414701&h=11529cec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=414701</a>"},{"pid":"469de2895f0f40d57f3f9b512918d161dd3e4beb","tid":2304840,"uid":212,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T07:04:53.000Z","msg":"易過抽農夫山泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b376742c2880b4bbd9ff17c49ef59c0eaac0c6b8","tid":2304840,"uid":289946,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"果時補埋地價計好似成22~23k一呎喎<br />\n而家有冇平到?🤔🤔"},{"pid":"c19217f66fd7f744ed3d307acd79824dfaa6d029","tid":2304840,"uid":220309,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:28:37.000Z","msg":"市建局AA做市<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2109b4c9838d58b8b36f3f113932a65cc9d582","tid":2304840,"uid":171611,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"樓爆喎，下年買平3-4成"},{"pid":"c12b39f88e6a31a3e0bb9a5151e381f95be9c1ca","tid":2304840,"uid":72825,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa2109b4c9838d58b8b36f3f113932a65cc9d582","tid":2304840,"uid":171611,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"樓爆喎，下年買平3-4成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"唔會跌得咁急，我估計需要幾年時間跌大約3-4成"},{"pid":"7d3d95dc18da2f6781908ca5f77fda8bdfdf61eb","tid":2304840,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:47:34.000Z","msg":"淨返全部3房？<br />\n<br />\n我記得計劃以外大單位正價賣唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73d841accdcfe2b4a846bc9bf856a367148955a","tid":2304840,"uid":240670,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"所以咪再9up 經濟差樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十年前,9up 中國乜乜省負債<br />\n乜乜企業無力償還貸款<br />\n經濟差,香港不能獨善其身<br />\n就9up 爛船都有三斤釘<br />\n隔一排香港樓價會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到兩年前貿易戰又9up 香港受到拖累<br />\n會經濟差,樓市跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到上年反送中港共又話有暴徒<br />\n藍屍又話無人嚴正執法<br />\n社會動盪,又9up 樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到今年年頭中國送大禮<br />\n又話肺炎死好多人,乜柒群組大爆發<br />\n全世界經濟收皮<br />\n又9up 樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到年中立國安法<br />\n又話投資者對香港前景唔明朗<br />\n會撤資,又9up 樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9up 左十年, 天災人禍乜柒都出曬嚟<br />\n香港樓價咪又係繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就新樓超額認購xx倍<br />\n一係就二手屋苑成交創新高<br />\n所以咪再話香港樓價會跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得世界大戰出核彈定外星人攻打地球<br />\n香港樓價都係繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee9d7e9018265051dbb989ab248a20f39873c3d","tid":2304840,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:36:42.000Z","msg":"樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5de69664d16aa41698aa990e54c7775c282f50","tid":2304840,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"呢4900人係月入33000或以上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0612a3c371d16b08998fd68a2ae11b499d36f3e","tid":2304840,"uid":119313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:59:42.000Z","msg":"都幾懷疑有一半係白撞，可能當咗居屋咁抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmo